[section#over.match.ref
    [:en] Initialization by conversion function for direct reference binding
    [:zh_CN] 直接引用绑定中通过转换函数进行初始化

[%[:en] overloading[!resolution[!initialization]]
  [:zh_CN] 重载[!～决议[!初始化]] ]
]

[para]
[:en]
Under the conditions specified in [#dcl.init.ref], a reference can be bound
directly to the result of applying a conversion function to an initializer
expression.
[:zh_CN]
在 [#dcl.init.ref] 中指定的条件下，引用可以被直接绑定到对初始化式表达式应用转换
函数的结果上。

[:en]
Overload resolution is used to select the conversion function to be invoked.
[:zh_CN]
使用重载决议来选择所要调用的转换函数。

[:en]
Assuming that [=lq]reference to [$cv1] [`T][=rq] is the type of the reference
being initialized, and [=lq][$cv] [`S][=rq] is the type of the initializer
expression, with [`S] a class type, the candidate functions are selected as
follows:
[:zh_CN]
假定“[$cv1] [`T] 的引用”为所初始化的引用，“[$cv] [`S]”为初始化式表达式的类型，
其中 [`S] 为类类型，其候选函数选择如下：

[list]
[item]
[:en]
The conversion functions of [`S] and its base classes are considered.
[:zh_CN]
考虑 [`S] 及其基类的转换函数。

[:en]
Those non-explicit conversion functions that are not hidden within [`S] and
yield type [=lq]lvalue reference to [$cv2] [`T2][=rq] (when initializing an
lvalue reference or an rvalue reference to function) or [=lq][$cv2] [`T2][=rq]
or [=lq]rvalue reference to [$cv2] [`T2][=rq] (when initializing an rvalue
reference or an lvalue reference to function), where [=lq][$cv1] [`T][=rq] is
reference-compatible ([#dcl.init.ref]) with [=lq][$cv2] [`T2][=rq], are
candidate functions.
[:zh_CN]
其中在 [`S] 之中未被隐藏，且产生类型“[$cv2] [`T2] 的左值引用”（当对左值引用或
函数的右值引用进行初始化时），或者“[$cv2] [`T2]”或“[$cv2] [`T2] 的右值引用”（当
对右值引用或函数的左值引用进行初始化时），其中“[$cv1] [`T]”与“[$cv2] [`T2]”引用
兼容（[#dcl.init.ref]），这样的非显式转换函数是候选函数。

[:en]
For direct-initialization, those explicit conversion functions that are not
hidden within [`S] and yield type [=lq]lvalue reference to [$cv2] [`T2][=rq]
(when initializing an lvalue reference or an rvalue reference to function) or
[=lq]rvalue reference to [$cv2] [`T2][=rq] (when initializing an rvalue
reference or an lvalue reference to function), where [`T2] is the same type as
[`T] or can be converted to type [`T] with a qualification conversion
([#conv.qual]), are also candidate functions.
[:zh_CN]
对于直接初始化，在 [`S] 之中未被隐藏，且（当初始化左值引用或函数的右值引用时）
产生类型“[$cv2] [`T2] 的左值引用”或（当初始化右值引用或函数的左值引用时）类型
“[$cv2] [`T2] 的右值引用”，其中 [`T2] 是与 [`T] 相同的类型，或可经由限定转换
（[#conv.qual]）转换为类型 [`T] 的类型，这样的显式转换函数也是候选函数。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en]
The argument list has one argument, which is the initializer expression.
[:zh_CN]
实参列表有一个实参，就是其初始化式表达式。

[begin:note]
[:en]
This argument will be compared against the implicit object parameter of the
conversion functions.
[:zh_CN]
此实参将与转换函数的隐含对象形参进行比较。
[end:note]
